snippet.title: [PS2] Jojo's Bizarre Adventure: Phantom Blood (2006) Full Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Here is a gameplay trailer for the 2006 Phantom Blood video game for PS2, this is unrelated to the 2007 Phantom Blood film aside from a couple of voice actors.
